; ------------------------------------------------------------
; Dog slowdown after finish (shared)
; ------------------------------------------------------------
; SET_OTHER_EXECUTOR_PTR installs this on all 6 dog slots once
; the race distance is covered -- dogs coast to a stop.

.dog_slowdown_after_finish:
    SET_FRAME_DELTA -8, 0, 0, 60
    DEACTIVATE_SELF

; ------------------------------------------------------------
; Finish-order tracker (executor 33, during the race)
; ------------------------------------------------------------
; finishLine holds the "finish-line" threshold (decrementing from 544);
; each frame, checks whether varN (the counter for dog N) has
; crossed finishLine, and if so writes the placement for dog N into
; gRaceFinishOrder. When two dogs are tied the ties are broken by
; jumping into the other dispatch to re-check. Deactivates once all 6
; positions are filled.

.race_track_finishers:
    SET_U16_VALUE 544, finishLine

