; ------------------------------------------------------------
; Finish-order resolver (executor 24, after the race)
; ------------------------------------------------------------
; Spawned once all 6 dogs have crossed the line. For each of the
; 6 positions, checks whether any dog has a placement code already
; assigned there; otherwise it increments varN and sorts dogs by
; their var-counters to pick the winner at each position. The big
; block of permutation branches below handles every dog-vs-dog
; comparison. Writes final placements to gRaceFinishOrder[2..5].

